Name: KUTCHINA KADHAI 22 CM
Short description: Time to bring home a lifestyle of healthy and hassle-free cooking with Kutchina’s Endura Cookware range. The cookware is made with a strong and safe 4-layered advanced Nano technology that helps you to maintain the family’s good health. The coating is not just long-lasting but metal spoon friendly as well. Alongside, the beautiful soft touch handles, induction compatible base and an exquisite marble finish make sure that cooking for you, is a delightful experience.
